				\begin{document}$$E=20\,{\rm{keV}}$$\end{document} with the exception of a-Se, reachable sensitivities of folded and conventional detectors are comparable, independently whether polycrystalline or single crystal conversion materials are utilized and the required layer thicknesses in the conventional layout are in the practicable range of d∈[100μm,750μm]\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
